				<p class="project-info">For an HCI Studio Design course, I worked with two other students to design and build a web app.  Our assignment was to create an app which could solve a communication problem using rich media.  We chose to create <strong>SoundBoard</strong>, a platform which helps amateur musicians connect and exchange feedback through live video practice sessions.  As the Design Lead for SoundBoard, I was responsible for establishing much of the look and feel of the app.  My team and I also held several rounds of user testing which we used to pivot our design and refine the app's usability.  <br><br>Our efforts earned us the <strong>Judges' Choice Award</strong> at our final project fair.</p>
